{"tid":1153070,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食片皮鴨食到想嘔","createTime":"2019-05-13T11:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:34:37.000Z","uid":18138,"like":35,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0990b155a9790ead1e9a2f6a92d0edccc28d41d7","tid":1153070,"uid":18138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:41:54.000Z","msg":"帶左雙親去食北京x家 食片皮鴨<br />\n叫左一隻鴨 雙親每人食左幾塊就話夠啦 <br />\n結果得返我係到係咁食 隻鴨我由頭食到尾 其他乜都冇食過，家下好想嘔 仲搞到我對鴨有少少陰影<br />\n原來自己一個人食一隻鴨 真係好難頂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a2d167488aeb5a6f6efc2ac9b0416ac0d34ed5","tid":1153070,"uid":113373,"like":16,"dislike":10,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:45:20.000Z","msg":"民主派議員上次曾率先佔據的立法會2樓兩大會議室（會議室一和會議室二），目前均已被立法會保安特別加上多條鐵鏈鎖上，意味民主派要如上周五般，率先進入會議室「霸房」已變得不可能。<br />\n<br />\n=====================<br />\n下次會議日期: 5月14日 （星期二）早上 8:15<br />\n<br />\n=====================<br />\n民陣「反惡法」活動<br />\n【通宵留守】<br />\n日期：5月13日（星期一）<br />\n時間：晚上11時<br />\n地點：立法會外添美道<br />\n=====================<br />\n【特首辦抗議】<br />\n日期：5月14日（星期二）<br />\n時間：早上8時<br />\n地點：特首辦門外<br />\n【立法會外集會】<br />\n=====================<br />\n日期：5月14日（星期二）<br />\n時間：早上8時<br />\n地點：立法會示威區，直播法案委員會情況<br />\n資"},{"pid":"d9a663dfde90d6e0962f7956256221cd39b3721e","tid":1153070,"uid":218674,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"片皮鴨最好食係第一啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374712f6d45967d11d94858c894bfcfb346dadc9","tid":1153070,"uid":42526,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSkzHck.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSkzHck.png&h=e4391b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗起呢個"},{"pid":"c67026d649951b4b96fbc11acd50bad9c91e5120","tid":1153070,"uid":186844,"like":1